Survey Render is a direct HST cutout to survey-like image renderer.

This repository does not vendor SLSim and does not generate SLSim lens/source
populations. It is intended to produce survey-like degraded renderings of
existing HST image cutouts.

Credit note: the broader lens simulation workflow that motivated this renderer
uses SLSim, the LSST Strong Lensing Simulation pipeline. If this renderer is
used alongside SLSim-generated data or in comparisons to that pipeline, cite and
acknowledge SLSim:

SLSim project: https://github.com/LSST-strong-lensing/slsim
SLSim documentation: https://slsim.readthedocs.io
SLSim license: MIT

Also cite and follow the usage terms for the HST/COSMOS or other survey data
products used as renderer inputs.
